@startuml System Flow
title MFSD System Flow Diagram

actor "Temperature Sensor" as Sensor
actor "Operator" as Operator

rectangle "Controller\n(REST Endpoint)" as Controller
rectangle "Service\n(Business Logic)" as Service
rectangle "Repository\n(Data Access Layer)" as Repository
database "Database\n(Temperature Readings)" as DB

Sensor --> Controller : Sends temperature data
Controller --> Service : Calls
Service --> Repository : Persists data
Repository --> DB : Stores readings
Service --> Controller : Returns result / triggers alert
Controller --> Operator : Alert / Response

@enduml